---
import BlogLayout from '../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
---

<BlogLayout title="Home">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Oasis: The Definitive History</h1>
    
    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xl mb-6">
        Oasis, formed in Manchester in 1991, became one of the most influential and commercially successful bands in British music history. Led by the Gallagher brothers, Noel and Liam, they defined the Britpop era of the 1990s.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Quick Facts</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Total Albums: 7 studio albums</li>
          <li>Singles: 28 UK singles</li>
          <li>Total Sales: Over 75 million records worldwide</li>
          <li>UK Number Ones: 8 singles, 8 albums</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Most Successful Album</h3>
          <p>(What's the Story) Morning Glory? (1995)</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Over 22 million copies sold worldwide</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Biggest Single</h3>
          <p>Wonderwall (1995)</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Over 1.3 million copies sold in the UK</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Explore More</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/albums" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Albums</h3>
          <p>Explore their complete discography</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/singles" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Singles</h3>
          <p>Chart history and statistics</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/statistics" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Statistics</h3>
          <p>Sales figures and achievements</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>